{"tid":482566,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"占士金馬倫：如果《阿凡達2、3》仆街就無《阿凡達4、5》","createTime":"2017-11-28T09:28:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T03:32:25.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"0a70dcd04a066c50fea5e6bf3f101c8b60f940b3","tid":482566,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T09:28:04.000Z","msg":"日前，導演占士金馬倫在採訪中表示，對於《阿凡達》是否還會有第3、4部，取決於《阿凡達2》的票房。20世紀霍士為《阿凡達》的續集投資了10億美元的預算，但如果票房失敗的話將會縮短整個計劃，並沒有給予過多的創作自由。<br />\n<br />\n對此，金馬倫表示自己已經面對現實，&ldquo;如果《阿凡達》的2、3部沒能賺到足夠多的錢，那麼就不會有第4和第5部了。&rdquo;據悉，《阿凡達》第2、3部將會一起拍攝，之後按照順序進行後期製作。如果霍士對票房不滿意，那《阿凡達》此後將再無續集。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.gooread.com/article/20124878718/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gooread.com%2Farticle%2F20124878718%2F&d=y%2BZDlISUvbTxSxmXlt41VYM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=2f845c06\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.gooread.com/article/20124878718/</a>"},{"pid":"1984a342ec3b21919606fdb0586910638aa0f948","tid":482566,"uid":4586,"like":15,"dislike":17,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T09:31:58.000Z","msg":"1已經垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b2409174c9a4e27caf5438b5cf9a415a4c2141","tid":482566,"uid":19867,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T09:35:40.000Z","msg":"你拍得好咪有票房囉on9<br />\n講到票房低既話係觀眾責任咁"},{"pid":"a9e3cf696b58de27dc1e37aa11aa41b153db7c9f","tid":482566,"uid":3369,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T09:37:06.000Z","msg":"自阿凡達開始咩戲都話搞3D，<br />\n但都冇一套有佢咁震撼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be3a335612f4b8d7b1a60474ed487db06ade3d66","tid":482566,"uid":7262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T09:44:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1已經垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當年既價錢入去睇3D 已經抵到爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n劇情垃唔垃圾 見仁見智"},{"p